{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Contagious is a good word."},{"time":3000,"text":"Even in the times of H1N1, I like the word."},{"time":7000,"text":"Laughter is contagious. Passion is contagious."},{"time":10000,"text":"Inspiration is contagious."},{"time":12000,"text":"We've heard some remarkable stories from some remarkable speakers."},{"time":17000,"text":"But for me, what was contagious about all of them"},{"time":20000,"text":"was that they were infected by something I call the"},{"time":23000,"text":"\"I Can\" bug."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25000,"text":"So, the question is, why only them?"},{"time":28000,"text":"In a country of a billion people and some,"},{"time":31000,"text":"why so few?"},{"time":33000,"text":"Is it luck? Is it chance?"},{"time":35000,"text":"Can we all not systematically and consciously"},{"time":37000,"text":"get infected?"},{"time":39000,"text":"So, in the next eight minutes I would like to share with you my story."},{"time":43000,"text":"I got infected when I was 17,"},{"time":45000,"text":"when, as a student of the design college,"},{"time":47000,"text":"I encountered adults who actually believed in my ideas,"},{"time":51000,"text":"challenged me and had lots of cups of chai with me."},{"time":54000,"text":"And I was struck by just how wonderful it felt,"},{"time":57000,"text":"and how contagious that feeling was."},{"time":59000,"text":"I also realized I should have got infected when I was seven."}]},{"cues":[{"time":64000,"text":"So, when I started Riverside school 10 years ago it became a lab,"},{"time":67000,"text":"a lab to prototype and refine a design process"},{"time":72000,"text":"that could consciously infect the mind with the \"I Can\" bug."},{"time":75000,"text":"And I uncovered"},{"time":77000,"text":"that if learning is embedded in real-world context,"},{"time":80000,"text":"that if you blur the boundaries between school and life,"},{"time":83000,"text":"then children go through a journey of \"aware,\""},{"time":86000,"text":"where they can see the change,"},{"time":88000,"text":"\"enable,\" be changed,"},{"time":91000,"text":"and then \"empower,\" lead the change."},{"time":94000,"text":"And that directly increased student wellbeing."},{"time":97000,"text":"Children became more competent,"},{"time":99000,"text":"and less helpless."},{"time":101000,"text":"But this was all common sense."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103000,"text":"So, I'd like to show you a little glimpse of what"},{"time":105000,"text":"common practice looks like at Riverside."},{"time":108000,"text":"A little background: when my grade five was learning about child rights,"},{"time":112000,"text":"they were made to roll incense sticks,"},{"time":114000,"text":"agarbattis, for eight hours"},{"time":116000,"text":"to experience what it means to be a child laborer."},{"time":120000,"text":"It transformed them. What you will see is their journey,"},{"time":122000,"text":"and then their utter conviction"},{"time":124000,"text":"that they could go out and change the world."},{"time":127000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":131000,"text":"That's them rolling."},{"time":133000,"text":"And in two hours, after their backs were broke,"},{"time":136000,"text":"they were changed."},{"time":138000,"text":"And once that happened,"},{"time":140000,"text":"they were out in the city convincing everybody"},{"time":143000,"text":"that child labor just had to be abolished."},{"time":148000,"text":"And look at Ragav, that moment when his face changes"},{"time":151000,"text":"because he's been able to understand that he"},{"time":154000,"text":"has shifted that man's mindset."},{"time":157000,"text":"And that can't happen in a classroom."},{"time":163000,"text":"So, when Ragav experienced that"},{"time":164000,"text":"he went from \"teacher told me,\""},{"time":167000,"text":"to \"I am doing it.\" And that's the \"I Can\" mindshift."},{"time":170000,"text":"And it is a process that can be energized and nurtured."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174000,"text":"But we had parents who said,"},{"time":176000,"text":"\"Okay, making our children good human beings is all very well,"},{"time":178000,"text":"but what about math and science and English?"},{"time":180000,"text":"Show us the grades.\""},{"time":182000,"text":"And we did. The data was conclusive."},{"time":185000,"text":"When children are empowered,"},{"time":187000,"text":"not only do they do good,"},{"time":189000,"text":"they do well, in fact very well,"},{"time":192000,"text":"as you can see in this national benchmarking assessment"},{"time":194000,"text":"taken by over 2,000 schools in India,"},{"time":197000,"text":"Riverside children were outperforming the top 10 schools in India"},{"time":200000,"text":"in math, English and science."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202000,"text":"So, it worked. It was now time to take it outside Riverside."},{"time":206000,"text":"So, on August 15th, Independence Day, 2007,"},{"time":210000,"text":"the children of Riverside set out to infect Ahmedabad."},{"time":215000,"text":"Now it was not about Riverside school."},{"time":217000,"text":"It was about all children. So, we were shameless."},{"time":220000,"text":"We walked into the offices of the municipal corporation, the police,"},{"time":223000,"text":"the press, businesses,"},{"time":225000,"text":"and basically said, \"When are you going to wake up"},{"time":228000,"text":"and recognize the potential that resides in every child?"},{"time":231000,"text":"When will you include the child in the city?"},{"time":233000,"text":"Basically, open your hearts and your minds to the child.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":236000,"text":"So, how did the city respond?"},{"time":238000,"text":"Since 2007 every other month"},{"time":241000,"text":"the city closes down the busiest streets for traffic"},{"time":245000,"text":"and converts it into a playground for children and childhood."},{"time":248000,"text":"Here was a city telling its child, \"You can.\""},{"time":252000,"text":"A glimpse of infection in Ahmedabad."},{"time":254000,"text":"Video: [Unclear]"},{"time":260000,"text":"So, the busiest streets closed down."},{"time":262000,"text":"We have the traffic police and municipal corporation helping us."},{"time":266000,"text":"It gets taken over by children."},{"time":269000,"text":"They are skating. They are doing street plays."},{"time":272000,"text":"They are playing, all free, for all children."},{"time":277000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":287000,"text":"Atul Karwal: aProCh is an organization which has been doing things for kids earlier."},{"time":290000,"text":"And we plan to extend this to other parts of the city."},{"time":292000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":295000,"text":"Kiran Bir Sethi: And the city will give free time."},{"time":298000,"text":"And Ahmedabad got the first child-friendly zebra crossing in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303000,"text":"Geet Sethi: When a city gives to the children,"},{"time":305000,"text":"in the future the children will give back to the city."},{"time":308000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":314000,"text":"KBS: And because of that,"},{"time":316000,"text":"Ahmedabad is known as India's first child-friendly city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320000,"text":"So, you're getting the pattern. First 200 children at Riverside."},{"time":323000,"text":"Then 30,000 children in Ahmedabad, and growing."},{"time":325000,"text":"It was time now to infect India."},{"time":329000,"text":"So, on August 15th,"},{"time":331000,"text":"again, Independence Day, 2009,"},{"time":334000,"text":"empowered with the same process,"},{"time":336000,"text":"we empowered 100,000 children to say, \"I can.\""},{"time":341000,"text":"How? We designed a simple toolkit,"},{"time":343000,"text":"converted it into eight languages,"},{"time":345000,"text":"and reached 32,000 schools."},{"time":348000,"text":"We basically gave children a very simple challenge."},{"time":350000,"text":"We said, take one idea,"},{"time":352000,"text":"anything that bothers you,"},{"time":354000,"text":"choose one week,"},{"time":356000,"text":"and change a billion lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":358000,"text":"And they did. Stories of change"},{"time":360000,"text":"poured in from all over India,"},{"time":363000,"text":"from Nagaland in the east,"},{"time":365000,"text":"to Jhunjhunu in the west,"},{"time":367000,"text":"from Sikkim in the north, to Krishnagiri in the south."},{"time":370000,"text":"Children were designing solutions for a diverse range of problems."},{"time":373000,"text":"Right from loneliness to filling potholes in the street"},{"time":377000,"text":"to alcoholism,"},{"time":379000,"text":"and 32 children who stopped 16 child marriages"},{"time":381000,"text":"in Rajasthan."},{"time":383000,"text":"I mean, it was incredible."},{"time":385000,"text":"Basically again reaffirming that when adults believe in children"},{"time":388000,"text":"and say, \"You can,\" then they will."},{"time":391000,"text":"Infection in India."},{"time":394000,"text":"This is in Rajasthan, a rural village."}]},{"cues":[{"time":396000,"text":"Child: Our parents are illiterate and we want to teach them how to read and write."},{"time":405000,"text":"KBS: First time, a rally and a street play in a rural school --"},{"time":408000,"text":"unheard of -- to tell their parents why literacy is important."},{"time":416000,"text":"Look at what their parents says."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420000,"text":"Man: This program is wonderful."},{"time":423000,"text":"We feel so nice that our children can teach us how to read and write."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427000,"text":"Woman: I am so happy that my students did this campaign."},{"time":430000,"text":"In the future, I will never doubt my students' abilities."},{"time":433000,"text":"See? They have done it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":437000,"text":"KBS: An inner city school in Hyderabad."},{"time":439000,"text":"Girl: 581. This house is 581 ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442000,"text":"We have to start collecting from 555."}]},{"cues":[{"time":445000,"text":"KBS: Girls and boys in Hyderabad, going out,"},{"time":447000,"text":"pretty difficult, but they did it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451000,"text":"Woman: Even though they are so young, they have done such good work."},{"time":455000,"text":"First they have cleaned the society, then it will be Hyderabad, and soon India."}]},{"cues":[{"time":462000,"text":"Woman: It was a revelation for me. It doesn't strike me"},{"time":465000,"text":"that they had so much inside them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468000,"text":"Girl: Thank you, ladies and gentlemen."},{"time":470000,"text":"For our auction we have some wonderful paintings for you,"},{"time":473000,"text":"for a very good cause,"},{"time":475000,"text":"the money you give us will be used to buy hearing aids."},{"time":478000,"text":"Are you ready, ladies and gentlemen? Audience: Yes!"},{"time":481000,"text":"Girl: Are you ready? Audience: Yes!"},{"time":483000,"text":"Girl: Are you ready? Audience: Yes!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":487000,"text":"KBS: So, the charter of compassion starts right here."},{"time":489000,"text":"Street plays, auctions, petitions."},{"time":492000,"text":"I mean, they were changing lives."},{"time":495000,"text":"It was incredible."},{"time":497000,"text":"So, how can we still stay immune?"},{"time":499000,"text":"How can we stay immune to that passion, that energy, that excitement?"},{"time":503000,"text":"I know it's obvious,"},{"time":505000,"text":"but I have to end with the most powerful symbol of change, Gandhiji."},{"time":509000,"text":"70 years ago, it took one man"},{"time":511000,"text":"to infect an entire nation"},{"time":513000,"text":"with the power of \"We can.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":516000,"text":"So, today who is it going to take"},{"time":518000,"text":"to spread the infection from 100,000 children"},{"time":521000,"text":"to the 200 million children in India?"},{"time":524000,"text":"Last I heard, the preamble still said, \"We, the people of India,\" right?"},{"time":528000,"text":"So, if not us, then who?"},{"time":530000,"text":"If not now, then when?"},{"time":533000,"text":"Like I said, contagious is a good word."},{"time":536000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":538000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}